										<tbody>
											<tr>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" width="25">&nbsp;</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 120px;" valign="top" width="542">
												<p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>All About Interviews</strong></span></p>

												<p>Hello and welcome to the latest edition of the Step Forward newsletter. This time we take a close look at employer interviews and what they&rsquo;re all about. We&rsquo;re going to hear from people who have already done them and give you the inside scoop on how to make sure you get the job. Here we go!</p>

												<div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
												<div align="center"><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#FFA500;"><strong><em>&ldquo;Be passionate about the organisation and let your enthusiasm and confidence shine through&rdquo;</em></strong></span></span></div>

												<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#FFA500;">- Sophie Drechsler, Operations Officer and Exeutive Assistant to the CEO</span></span></div>

												<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#FFA500;">Step Up To Serve</span></span></div>
												</div>
												</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" width="25">&nbsp;</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" width="25">&nbsp;</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 120px; width: 300px;" valign="top">
												<p><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Let The Step Forward Interviews Begin!</strong></span></p>

												<p>You&rsquo;ve done the assessments, you&rsquo;ve written your CV and now it&rsquo;s time for the Step Forward interviews. This month, we had the first of our employer matching events and it was a big success with many young people being offered roles for September. We sat down with young people on the day and asked them a few questions so that you can know what to expect.</p>
												<img alt="" src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C0000002XWQM&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f&amp;lastMod=1421164033000" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 5px; height: 440px; float: left;" />
												<div>
												<div><img alt="" src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C0000002XWQM&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f&amp;lastMod=1421164033000" style="width: 5px; height: 440px; float: right;" /></div>
												</div>

												<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 230px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
													<tbody>
														<tr>
															<td>
															<div><img alt="" src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C0000002sF63&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f&amp;lastMod=1432290208000" style="width: 210px; height: 63px;" /></div>
															</td>
														</tr>
													</tbody>
												</table>

												<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 510px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
													<tbody>
														<tr>
															<td>
															<div style="text-align: right;">
															<ul>
																<li style="text-align: left;">&#39;I went over my CV and job description. I planned almost everything I possibly could: travel plan, the organisations, practising CAR&#39;.</li>
																<li style="text-align: left;">&#39;I did extensive research on the companies, e.g. read &nbsp;their website&#39;.</li>
																<li style="text-align: left;">&#39;I did mock interviews with my mum&#39;.</li>
																<li style="text-align: left;">&#39;I prepared several questions to ask the employers at the end of the interview&#39;.</li>
															</ul>
															</div>
															</td>
														</tr>
													</tbody>
												</table>

												<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; width: 230px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
													<tbody>
														<tr>
															<td><img alt="" src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C0000002sF68&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f&amp;lastMod=1432290230000" style="width: 236px; height: 71px;" /></td>
														</tr>
													</tbody>
												</table>

												<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 510px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
													<tbody>
														<tr>
															<td>
															<div style="text-align: right;">
															<ul>
																<li style="text-align: left;">&#39;The company love when you show enthusiasm, so researching into them will go a long way&#39;.</li>
																<li style="text-align: left;">&#39;Don&rsquo;t assume the interviewer will be tough on you. They&rsquo;re serious but friendly too&#39;!</li>
																<li style="text-align: left;">&#39;Expect to be nervous, it&rsquo;s normal and expect lots of questions, it&rsquo;s an interview&#39;!</li>
															</ul>
															</div>
															</td>
														</tr>
													</tbody>
												</table>

												<p>All excellent advice. You&rsquo;ll hear from us in the next few months with an invitation to &nbsp; interviews so until then, keep practising.&nbsp;</p>

												<div align="center"><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#FFA500;"><strong><em>&ldquo;Show a specific interest in the organisation. Try not to generalise&rdquo;</em></strong></span></span></div>

												<div align="right"><span style="color:#FFA500;">- Sharmila Fakun, HR Director, Marriott Hotels</span></div>
												</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" width="25">&nbsp;</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" width="25">&nbsp;</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 120px; width: 300px;" valign="top">
												<p><strong style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">A Success Story</strong></p>

												<p>We want to offer a huge <strong>congratulations</strong> to all our successful candidates at the first round of interviews! One of these is Mariam, who interviewed with the Business Services Association and is going to start her role as a Business Support Officer in September.&nbsp;We asked her what it was like on the day&hellip;</p>

												<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 450px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
													<tbody>
														<tr>
															<td>
															<p><strong>How did you find the day?&nbsp;</strong>I was nervous when I saw the other candidates and met the employer as this was&nbsp;my first interview.&nbsp;</p>

															<p><strong>How was the interview?&nbsp;</strong>It was surprisingly relaxed and the interviewer was really friendly. She asked about me a lot and it was more casual than I had prepared with my teacher.&nbsp;</p>

															<p><strong>How do you feel now?&nbsp;</strong>Really excited and happy to start!</p>
															</td>
															<td>
															<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><img alt="" src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C0000002sFEb&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f&amp;lastMod=1432293270000" style="width: 180px; height: 224px;" /></span></p>
															</td>
														</tr>
													</tbody>
												</table>

												<p>Well done Mariam! And well done to everyone who aced their interview!</p>

												<div align="center"><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#FFA500;"><strong><em>&ldquo;Tell a compelling story and be specific about the outcomes of your examples&rdquo;</em></strong></span></span></div>

												<div align="right"><span style="color:#FFA500;">- Melanie Maxwell-Scott, Director of Policy, Business Services Association</span></div>
												</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" width="25">&nbsp;</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" width="25">&nbsp;</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 65px; width: 300px;" valign="top">
												<p><b>We&#39;re here to help</b></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;">Speaking of acing an interview, we&rsquo;re here to help you prepare as much as you possibly can. We&rsquo;ve held an interview preparation event, helped you with your CV and we even made a video to help you on your way. Make sure you go back through everything we&rsquo;ve given you and put yourself in the best position to get the job.</span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;">We&rsquo;ve said that we&rsquo;re here to help and we really are. If you have any questions at all please get in touch. You can call us on <strong>020 3542 2404</strong>, email <a href="mailto:step.forward@the-challenge.org"><strong>step.forward@the-challenge.org</strong></a> or find us on <a href="http://www.facebook.com/thestepforward?ref=ts&amp;fref=ts" target="_blank">facebook</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="http://twitter.com/The_StepForward" target="_blank">twitter</a></span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;">We&rsquo;re going to leave you alone for a bit while you do your exams so for now&hellip;</span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;">Good luck!</span></p>

												<p><span style="font-size:14px;">Step Forward</span></p>

												<div align="center"><span style="font-size:18px;"><strong><em><span style="color:#FFA500;">&ldquo;Loosen up and be confident in yourself&rdquo;</span></em></strong></span></div>

												<div align="right"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color:#FFA500;">- Stephen Walker, Co-Founder and Director, Drew</span></span></div>
												</td>
												<td align="left" bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
											</tr>
